{"id":"orch-go-05ws","title":"Add /api/reflect endpoint for KB synthesis suggestions","description":"Surface reflect-suggestions.json data in web UI.\n\nData source: ~/.orch/reflect-suggestions.json\n- Generated by 'orch daemon reflect' or 'kb reflect'\n- Shows topics with multiple investigations needing consolidation\n\nCurrent data shows:\n- 'orch' topic: 29 investigations (!)\n- Other topics with 3+ investigations each\n\nEndpoint should return:\n- synthesis: topics needing consolidation (3+ investigations)\n- promote: kn entries ready for kb promotion\n- stale: decisions with 0 citations, \u003e7 days old\n- timestamp: when suggestions were generated\n\nUI usage:\n- 'Knowledge Debt' panel showing topics needing synthesis\n- Badge count of actionable items\n- Links to specific investigations\n\nThis surfaces 'what knowledge work is piling up' - helps prioritize documentation work.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-12-26T10:33:15.584872-08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-26T12:56:31.121278-08:00","closed_at":"2025-12-26T12:56:31.121278-08:00","close_reason":"Verified /api/reflect endpoint already implemented in commit 88b71037. Endpoint returns reflect-suggestions.json data with timestamp and synthesis array. Tests pass, documentation updated.","labels":["skill:feature-impl","triage:ready"]}
