{"id":"orch-go-1bkbm","title":"Add bd graph --all CLI option","description":"Export full dependency graph as JSON via CLI.\n\n**Usage:** bd graph --all --json\n\n**Output:** Same structure as /api/beads/graph endpoint - all nodes + edges with authority.\n\n**Why:** Debugging, scripting, parity with API.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-23T09:48:50.694559-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-24T10:05:05.3172-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-24T10:05:05.3172-08:00","close_reason":"Phase: Complete - Added bd graph --all CLI option. Tests: go test ./cmd/bd/... -run Graph - 7 tests passed. Committed to beads repo: feat(cli): add bd graph --all for full dependency graph export","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"orch-go-1bkbm","depends_on_id":"orch-go-5ubkd","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-24T00:34:51.260967-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","authority":"daemon"}]}
{"id":"orch-go-1c5ov","title":"Implement session end validation + interactive completion (Capture at Context)","description":"Implement validation gate and interactive completion for orch session end per Capture at Context principle.\n\n## Context\n- Decision: .kb/decisions/2026-01-14-capture-at-context.md\n- Problem: Handoffs incomplete because gate fires at wrong moment (end vs throughout)\n- Current: promptForSessionSummary only asks Outcome + Brief Summary\n- Need: Validate all sections, prompt for unfilled ones\n\n## Design (approved by Dylan)\n\n### Sections to validate (with placeholder patterns):\n1. Outcome - {success | partial | blocked | failed} (required)\n2. TLDR - [Fill within first 5 tool calls:...] (required)\n3. Where We Ended - {state of focus goal now} (required)  \n4. Next Recommendation - {continue-focus | shift-focus | escalate | pause} (required)\n5. Evidence - [Pattern 1: e.g., (optional, allow 'nothing notable')\n6. Knowledge - {topic}: (optional, allow 'none')\n7. Friction - [Tool gap or UX issue] (optional, allow 'smooth')\n\n### Flow:\n1. validateHandoff() - check which sections have placeholders\n2. promptForUnfilledSections() - interactive prompts for each\n3. updateHandoffWithResponses() - replace placeholders\n4. Archive only when complete\n\n### Files to modify:\n- cmd/orch/session.go - replace promptForSessionSummary with new validation system\n- Remove old updateHandoffTemplate function\n- Update runSessionEnd to use new completeAndArchiveHandoff function\n\n## Tests needed:\n- Test validation detects unfilled sections\n- Test interactive completion flow\n- Test placeholder replacement","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-14T12:49:59.285397-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-14T13:02:21.979855-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-14T13:02:21.979855-08:00","close_reason":"Session end validation implemented. Tests verified: TestValidateHandoff*, TestUpdateHandoffWithResponses, TestHandoffSectionsDefinition - all PASS"}
