{"id":"orch-go-1u771","title":"Synthesize synthesis investigations (24)","description":"## Synthesis Needed\n\nTopic **synthesis** has accumulated 24 investigations that may benefit from consolidation.\n\n### Investigations to synthesize:\n\n- 2025-12-20-audit-legacy-artifacts-synthesis-protocol.md\n- 2025-12-20-design-synthesis-protocol-schema.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-implement-synthesis-card-display-swarm.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-implement-synthesis-protocol-create-orch.md\n- 2025-12-21-inv-agents-skip-synthesis-md-creation.md\n- 2025-12-21-synthesis-registry-evolution-and-orch-identity.md\n- 2025-12-26-design-synthesis-review-workflow.md\n- 2025-12-26-inv-synthesis-review-view-parse-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-agent-investigations-17-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-api-investigations-11-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-beads-investigations-17-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-cli-investigations-16-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-dashboard-investigations-39-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-extract-investigations-11-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-headless-investigations-15-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-model-investigations-10-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-opencode-investigations-16-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-orchestrator-investigations-28-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-skill-investigations-15-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-spawn-investigations-36-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-06-inv-synthesize-tmux-investigations-11-synthesis.md\n- 2026-01-07-design-recurring-problem-duplicate-synthesis-issues.md\n- 2026-01-07-inv-orch-status-surface-synthesis-opportunities.md\n- 2025-12-20-inv-beta-flash-synthesis-protocol-design.md\n\n### Chronicle Timeline\n\n```\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI orch spawn Command Implementation\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI Orch Status Command\n2025-12-19 [INV] CLI Project Scaffolding and Build Setup\n2025-12-19 [INV] OpenCode Client Package Session Management\n2025-12-19 [INV] SSE Event Monitoring Client\n... (run kb chronicle for full timeline)\n```\n\n### Suggested Action\n\n1. Run `kb chronicle \"synthesis\"` to understand evolution\n2. Identify patterns and contradictions across investigations\n3. Create a synthesized decision or consolidated investigation\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-07T20:13:46.43079-08:00","updated_at":"2026-01-07T22:47:01.735921-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-07T22:47:01.735921-08:00","close_reason":"Bulk close: kb reflect synthesis noise","labels":["triage:review"]}
