{"id":"orch-go-20933","title":"[orch-go] investigation: OpenCode server keeps crashing/dying, killing s...","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-26T16:27:20.317466-08:00","created_by":"dylanconlin","updated_at":"2026-01-26T21:21:35.293235-08:00","closed_at":"2026-01-26T21:21:35.293235-08:00","comments":[{"id":1,"issue_id":"orch-go-20933","author":"dylanconlin","text":"Phase: Planning - Investigating OpenCode server crashes killing agent sessions","created_at":"2026-01-26T16:27:34.284336-08:00"},{"id":2,"issue_id":"orch-go-20933","author":"dylanconlin","text":"investigation_path: /Users/dylanconlin/Documents/personal/orch-go/.kb/investigations/2026-01-26-inv-opencode-server-keeps-crashing-dying.md","created_at":"2026-01-26T16:27:41.744444-08:00"},{"id":3,"issue_id":"orch-go-20933","author":"dylanconlin","text":"Phase: Complete - Investigation complete. Three failure modes identified: (1) unhandledRejection errors corrupt sessions but don't crash server, (2) SSE stream breaking when server crashes kills agents, (3) orch serve restart is independent of OpenCode. Recommended fixes: patch three OpenCode bugs + implement auto-resume mechanism from Jan 17 design. Investigation file: .kb/investigations/2026-01-26-inv-opencode-server-keeps-crashing-dying.md","created_at":"2026-01-26T16:33:27.629834-08:00"}]}
